## Prerequisites

- Terraform >= 1.0
- {{cloudProvider}} CLI configured
- Valid {{cloudProvider}} credentials

## Usage

### Initialize

```bash
terraform init
```

### Plan

```bash
terraform plan
```

### Apply

```bash
terraform apply
```

### Destroy

```bash
terraform destroy
```

## Structure

- `main.tf` - Main infrastructure definitions
- `variables.tf` - Input variables
- `outputs.tf` - Output values
- `terraform.tfvars` - Variable values (gitignored)

